<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<%
    const newsBase = (newsBasePath || "/tin-tuc").toString().trim().replace(/\/+$/, "") || "/tin-tuc";
    const pageTitle = (title || "Không tìm thấy trang").toString().trim();
%>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle %> | A-M News Việt Nam</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/logobfang.svg">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/logobfang.svg">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "Noto Sans JP", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 14% -10%, rgba(248, 248, 242, 0.1), transparent 34%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 84% 120%, rgba(248, 248, 242, 0.07), transparent 30%),
                #0c0c0c;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #f8f8f2;
            padding: 14px;
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(248, 248, 242, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 26px 26px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .error-container {
            width: min(560px, 100%);
            border: 1px solid #2b2b2b;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: #141414;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 34px 24px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.35s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(8px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 86px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            animation: bounce 1s ease infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-6px);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 34px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
            color: #b5b5b5;
        }

        .countdown {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
            color: #b5b5b5;
        }

        .countdown span {
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid #454545;
            background: #1d1d1d;
            color: #f8f8f2;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            margin: 0 4px;
            min-width: 44px;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            min-height: 38px;
            padding: 9px 18px;
            border: 1px solid #f8f8f2;
            background: #f8f8f2;
            color: #0c0c0c;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            opacity: 0.92;
        }

        .btn-home i {
            margin-right: 6px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .countdown {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .btn-home {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body data-news-base-path="<%= newsBase %>">
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>Oops! Không tìm thấy trang</h1>
        <p>Tin tức này có thể đã bị xóa hoặc link không đúng.</p>
        <div class="countdown">
            Tự động chuyển về trang tin tức sau <span id="countdown">3</span> giây
        </div>
        <a href="<%= newsBase %>" class="btn-home">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            Về Trang Tin tức
        </a>
    </div>

    <script nonce="<%= cspNonce || '' %>">
        let seconds = 3;
        const countdownElement = document.getElementById('countdown');

        const countdown = setInterval(() => {
            seconds -= 1;
            countdownElement.textContent = seconds;

            if (seconds <= 0) {
                clearInterval(countdown);
                window.location.href = '<%= newsBase %>';
            }
        }, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
